| containedby = owner = MapInfo extendedfrom = extendedto = standard =
}} 'MapInfo Interchange Format' is a map and database exporting file format of
MapInfo software product. The MIF-file filename usually ends with .mif-suffix.
Some MIF-files also have a related MID-file. The filename of a MID-file usually
ends with .mid-suffix.
